result.content: Hello. My problem is, that when I run the following code on my Mac, it works and produces the right output. When uploaded to the codeforces judge, It gives me the aforementioned error, and tells me that my program didn't output anything. I also tried compiling and running it on c++ shell, and with compiler optimisations turned off, it compiled and produced the right answer, but with full optimisation it also didn't output anything. Could I really have stumbled upon a compiler bug, or am I doing something really wrong?
